in your jurisdiction) for managing personal, legally-obtained media files.

The developers and contributors of this software:
- Do not host, distribute, or provide any media content
- Are not responsible for how users utilize this software
- Are not responsible for the content managed using this software
- Make no warranties about fitness for any particular purpose

Users are solely responsible for:
- Ensuring they have legal rights to all media they manage
